<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Another prior section 562, <ref href="/us/act/1949-08-04/ch393">act Aug. 4, 1949, ch. 393</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/63/539">63 Stat. 539</ref>; <ref href="/us/act/1950-08-03/ch536/s27">Aug. 3, 1950, ch. 536, § 27</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/64/407">64 Stat. 407</ref>, related to deck courts, prior to repeal by <ref href="/us/act/1950-05-05/ch169">act May 5, 1950, ch. 169</ref>, §§ 5, 14(v), <ref href="/us/stat/64/145">64 Stat. 145</ref>, 148, effective <date date="1951-05-31">May 31, 1951</date>.</p>
