<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id569cc6f9-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2018—<ref href="/us/pl/115/282">Pub. L. 115–282</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t14/s101">section 101 of this title</ref> as this section.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/115/232">Pub. L. 115–232</ref> substituted “Commandant” for “Commandant of the Coast Guard” in introductory provisions.</p>
